  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Engineering Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Engineering Manager / Lead Software Engineer</strong></p><p>This role is for someone who wants to shape technical strategy, and stay hands-on while building meaningful products.</p><p>You’ll work in an environment that feels like a modern product company: agile, collaborative, and focused on real outcomes; not just output.<br /></p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>Define and communicate the engineering vision and technical strategy</li><li>Partner with stakeholders to prioritize work and manage delivery roadmaps</li><li>Design long-term technical plans that scale with product and infrastructure needs</li><li>Mentor and grow engineers through feedback, coaching, and career development</li><li>Collaborate cross-functionally to ensure quality, reliability, and security</li><li>Lead initiatives that improve engineering effectiveness and team impact</li><li>Champion tools, practices, and culture that enable engineering excellence</li><li>Stay technically hands-on as part of the role</li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>8-10+ years of full stack software engineering experience, including DevOps exposure</li><li>Experience building and scaling high-availability software systems</li><li>Proficiency in modern full-stack technologies (ideally React, Next.js, TypeScript, Python, Golang, Java)</li><li>Strong technical leadership, with the soft skills needed to build trust and alignment</li><li>Passion for engineering excellence and thoughtful software craftsmanship</li><li>Motivation to create impact through technology</li><li>Proven ability to guide teams toward shared goals and outcomes</li><li>Comfortable remaining technically hands-on as part of the role</li><li>Experience leading, mentoring and supporting the growth of developers</li></ul><p>For more information you can contact <em>Norean Tan at norean.tan@sanderson-ikas.sg</em></p><p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be notified / contacted.<br /></p><p>EA Registration No.: R1434118 <em>- Tan Lee Ying, Norean</em></p><p>iKas International (Asia) Pte Ltd</p><p>ROC No.: 200914065E | EA License No.: 16S8086</p>",
